{"id":"24h-workers-1","title":"Heartbeat 独立工具开发","description":"开发一个独立的 heartbeat 工具，支持定时巡检 + tmux 注入。有两种运行模式：\n1. 独立模式（最小核心）：纯定时触发，无需代理\n2. 代理增强模式：拦截 finish_reason=stop 时额外触发\n\n核心功能：\n- 定时主循环（默认 15 分钟）\n- tmux 文本注入\n- 状态持久化\n- Clock 时间标签注入\n- CLI 命令\n\n技术栈：\n- TypeScript\n- Node.js \u003e=18\n- tmux 命令行工具","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"epic","owner":"bot@routecodex.com","created_at":"2026-03-16T18:13:20.045028+08:00","created_by":"RouteCodex Bot","updated_at":"2026-03-16T18:43:17.049791+08:00","closed_at":"2026-03-16T18:43:17.049791+08:00"}
{"id":"24h-workers-1.1","title":"实现 core/ 核心模块","description":"核心模块文件：\n- config.ts: 配置管理，解析与默认值\n- state-store.ts: session 状态持久化到 ~/.heartbeat/\n- trigger.ts: heartbeat 触发逻辑\n- daemon.ts: 定时主循环\n\n验收标准：\n- 配置可从文件和环境变量加载\n- 状态正确持久化和读取\n- daemon 可启动/停止\n- 触发逻辑正确调用 tmux 注入","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"RouteCodex Bot","owner":"bot@routecodex.com","created_at":"2026-03-16T18:13:57.849619+08:00","created_by":"RouteCodex Bot","updated_at":"2026-03-16T18:21:05.696927+08:00","closed_at":"2026-03-16T18:21:05.696927+08:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"24h-workers-1.1","depends_on_id":"24h-workers-1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"}]}
{"id":"24h-workers-1.2","title":"实现 tmux/ 模块","description":"tmux 模块文件：\n- injector.ts: tmux send-keys 文本注入\n- session-probe.ts: session 存活检测，获取工作目录\n\n验收标准：\n- 文本正确注入到 tmux session\n- session 存活状态检测准确\n- 工作目录正确获取","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"RouteCodex Bot","owner":"bot@routecodex.com","created_at":"2026-03-16T18:14:06.574611+08:00","created_by":"RouteCodex Bot","updated_at":"2026-03-16T18:19:50.19706+08:00","closed_at":"2026-03-16T18:19:50.19706+08:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"24h-workers-1.2","depends_on_id":"24h-workers-1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"}]}
{"id":"24h-workers-1.3","title":"实现 clock/ 模块","description":"clock 模块文件：\n- time-tag.ts: 生成时间标签\n\n验收标准：\n- 时间标签包含 utc/local/tz/nowMs\n- 格式符合 RouteCodex 规范","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"RouteCodex Bot","owner":"bot@routecodex.com","created_at":"2026-03-16T18:14:06.766354+08:00","created_by":"RouteCodex Bot","updated_at":"2026-03-16T18:19:50.464184+08:00","closed_at":"2026-03-16T18:19:50.464184+08:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"24h-workers-1.3","depends_on_id":"24h-workers-1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"}]}
{"id":"24h-workers-1.4","title":"实现 cli/ 命令","description":"CLI 命令实现：\n- heartbeat start: 启动 daemon\n- heartbeat start --with-proxy: 启动 daemon + 代理\n- heartbeat stop: 停止 daemon\n- heartbeat trigger -s \u003csession\u003e: 手动触发\n- heartbeat status: 查看状态\n- heartbeat list: 列出所有 session\n- heartbeat on -s \u003csession\u003e: 启用 session\n- heartbeat off -s \u003csession\u003e: 禁用 session\n\n验收标准：\n- 所有命令正确执行\n- 错误处理完善\n- 输出格式清晰","status":"closed","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","owner":"bot@routecodex.com","created_at":"2026-03-16T18:14:06.955573+08:00","created_by":"RouteCodex Bot","updated_at":"2026-03-16T18:21:05.83556+08:00","closed_at":"2026-03-16T18:21:05.83556+08:00","dependencies":[{"issue_id":"24h-workers-1.4","depends_on_id":"24h-workers-1","type":"parent-child","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"}]}
